## ததஅக

[ iṉpavupatai ]  
  
பெ. id. crucial test of the continence of a minister orother officer of state conducted sub rosa  
by aking  
which consists in his (the kings) sendingan old maid long in the service of the harem  
totempt the officer concerned  
with a story thatone of the queens is desperately in love withhim (the officer)  
and that not only great pleasurebut also splendid destiny await him if hewould meet the queens wishes  
one of fourupatai  
q.v.; உபதை நான்கனுள் ஒன்று. (குறள்  
501  
உரை.)